---
title: Herby Veggie Patties with Beyond Meat®,Creamy Mash and Leek Gravy
description: Savoury Beyond Meat sided with creamy mashed potatoes and sweet peas make for a tasty dish. This delicious classic is finished with gravy, and is a guaranteed household winner!
